\par }{\b\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 Features}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 
\par 
\par Dungeon Craft is an adventure creator that is based on the AD&D gaming system. It mimics the features and functionality of SSI's Forgotten Realms Unlimited Adventures.
\par 
\par While FRUA is DOS based, Dungeon Craft is Win32 based and currently runs under Windows 95/98/NT/2000 using DirectX 3.
\par 
\par Some improvements over the DOS based product have been made:
\par 
\par }{\f3\fs18\insrsid5405 \'b7}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 \tab supports 16/24/32 bit color
\par }{\f3\fs18\insrsid5405 \'b7}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 \tab supports BMP, PCX, TGA, JPG, PNG, WAV, MIDI, and MP3 file types
\par }{\f3\fs18\insrsid5405 \'b7}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 \tab 640x480, 800x600, and 1024x768 screen sizes
\par }{\f3\fs18\insrsid5405 \'b7}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 \tab Editable items, spells and monsters
\par }{\f3\fs18\insrsid5405 \'b7}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 \tab Increased capacity for maps, events, quests, special items, and text
\par }{\f3\fs18\insrsid5405 \'b7}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 \tab Each design is self-contained, the editor is not required to play the game
\par }{\f3\fs18\insrsid5405 \'b7}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 \tab All art can be customized
\par }{\f3\fs18\insrsid5405 \'b7}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 \tab Area view can be configured to auto map, display the whole map, or no map.
\par }{\f3\fs18\insrsid5405 \'b7}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 \tab Text events can be interactive with the player
\par }{\f3\fs18\insrsid5405 \'b7}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 \tab Powerful script engine allows map modifications at runtime
\par 
\par Plus, new features, event triggers, etc, can be added as desired. Just send me your suggestions.
\par 
