\par 
\par There are three ways to make your design available to others that I know of. 
\par 
\par 1. Make it available on your own website and announce it here, I'll then add a link to your site from the DC site to help others find it.
\par 
\par 2. Upload it to Ziroc's archive on this site.
\par 
\par http://www.tgeweb.com/ironworks/dungeoncraft/gamedesigns.shtml
\par 
\par 3. Upload it to the Magic Mirror. Mention that it is a DC design, since the MM stores DC and UA files.
