\par Entry Point Mode is used to place the 8 entry points for the current level.
\par 
\par }{\f1\fs18\cf6\insrsid5405 Starting Point Mode:  The Toolbar }{\f5\fs18\cf6\insrsid5405 "S"}{\f1\fs18\cf6\insrsid5405  }{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 
