\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 
\par }{\b\f1\fs18\cf17\insrsid5405 Moving Around Using Mouse}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 
\par 
\par You can jump to any square in your 2-d map by holding down the 'Control' key and clicking the mouse in that cell.
\par 
\par If you have '}{\f1\fs18\uldb\insrsid5405 KwikKlik}{\v\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 !KLink(KwikKlik)}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 ' enabled, you can use the mouse to move around the design.
\par 
\par The 3-d window is divided into 3 equal horizontal stripes; a top, a center, and a bottom stripe.  These stripes are not marked in any way but with a bit of practice you can locate them easily.  The center slice is used to place and delete walls.
\par 
\par You can move around your level by clicking the mouse in the top or bottom stripe, as follow:
\par 
\par }{\f1\fs18\cf6\insrsid5405 To turn left.}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405   Left-click the left one-third of the top stripe.
\par }{\f1\fs18\cf6\insrsid5405 To turn right.}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405   Left-click the right one-third of the top stripe.
\par }{\f1\fs18\cf6\insrsid5405 To turn around 180 degrees. }{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405  Left-click the center of the bottom stripe.
\par }{\f1\fs18\cf6\insrsid5405 To move forward without turning.}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405   Right-click the center of the top stripe.
\par }{\f1\fs18\cf6\insrsid5405 To move backward without turning.}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405   Right-click the center of the bottom stripe.
\par }{\f1\fs18\cf6\insrsid5405 To move left without turning.}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405   Right-click the left one-third of the top stripe.
\par }{\f1\fs18\cf6\insrsid5405 To move right without turning.}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405   Right-click the right one-third of the top stripe.
\par 
\par So the rule is simple.  Left-click to turn and right-click to move.
\par 
\par Note that you cannot move through blocked walls unless you enable 'Move Through Walls' in the 'Mode' menu.
\par 
\par See }{\f1\fs18\uldb\insrsid5405 Moving Around Using Arrows}{\v\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 !ALink(ArrowMove)}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 
