\par }{\b\f1\fs18\cf17\insrsid5405 Moving Around Using Arrow Keys}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 
\par 
\par The 'up' arrow key moves you forward one square.
\par The 'left' arrow key turns you left 90 degrees.
\par The 'right' arrow key turns you right 90 degrees.
\par The 'down' arrow key turns you left or right 180 degrees.  You decide.
\par 
\par 'Forward' means the direction you are facing.
\par 
\par Your current position and the direction you are facing in the level is indicated on the 2-d map by a small white arrow in one of the squares.
\par 
