\par Wall (default format) - 576x368
\par Sprite - 528x211
\par icons - multiple of 48, two frames, in order of ready, attack. 1x1=96x48
\par title - 640x480
\par backdrop, small pic - 176x211
\par map, big pic - 608x288
\par combat cursor - 48x48
\par combat dying icon - 48x48
\par combat death animation - 96x48, two frames that are alternated rapidly when a creature dies
\par 
\par The current image sizes for a 800x600 game engine screen are:
