\par }{\f1\fs18\cf6\insrsid5405 Cancel Button}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 
\par 
\par Pressing the "Cancel" button means that any changes you have made to any of the items since you opened this "Items Edit" window will be lost.  Be careful.
