\par Setting an entry point is as easy as setting a wall somewhere. Select }{\b\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 P}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405  from the toolbar to get into }{\i\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 Entry Point Mode}{\f1\fs18\insrsid5405 
